title: FOOTBALL: Chesaning loses to Alma

FOOTBALL: Chesaning loses to Alma The Argus-Press The Argus-Press | 0 comments 
ALMA — Chesaning couldn’t pull off an upset on the road as the Indians fell to Alma, 15-14.
